This is Jade Curtiss. I'm off elsewhere, so leave a message with the time you called and your number and I will get back to you as soon as I can.

Unless your name happens to be Dist The Runny, in which case, I'm screening my calls and completely ignoring you.

*Ping*

This is Jade Curtiss. I'm obviously not paying attention to this contraption right now, unless your brain can't comprehend that fact. Anyways, leave a message, 225 characters maximum.

And for the love of science no smiley faces or abbreviations or I will hunt you down personally and
